{"tid":918410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所謂泛民主派, 既不廣泛, 也不民主, 更非派別","createTime":"2018-11-27T07:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T20:26:24.000Z","uid":66324,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eda16260f92a4d179053912c12cef77cca0fbe7b","tid":918410,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">既不廣泛</span><br />\n--- 其實只係一堆大中華膠同和理非非, 激進少少或者有新的理念都會被打壓<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">也不民主</span><br />\n--- 望下plan B單野已經知<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更非派別</span><br />\n--- 雖然派別內部有唔同政見好正常, 但係所謂泛民根本連基本的紀律同合作都無, 2012年公民黨企圖推名單第二名的人入局, 民主黨李永達陳樹英兩公婆攬炒 (雖然我覺得公民黨都有份造成)<br />\n2016 年馮檢基無故空降新西 (呢個真係有問題, 佢可以選九西或者排第二保住九西果席, 2012 年果陣譚國僑已經輸Q左, 根本唔應該咁大貪, 唔係下下都好似新東D選民咁醒咁勁<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多單野都罊竹難書, 請各位連登巴打補充"},{"pid":"1e0edd7842dc8dde3f558d4799e94b4b291b212b","tid":918410,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9b9ac85f43e8cc8d8ea74c74beda4627b65da0","tid":918410,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f012eba89b659204ee47a9a7fa9c529a9c527150","tid":918410,"uid":127929,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"只係一班貪份糧等人養而千方百計阻止後生仔上位既老屎忽"},{"pid":"cc9b18d0d783c9862862ba5e24c58be23abb55e5","tid":918410,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"2016 年馮檢基無故空降新西<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連燈仔話佢唔算空降㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i